military alliance 
solidarity was the east blocs first independent trade union when 
it was formed in 1980 by walesa 
it was legal for 16 months and its membership ballooned to 10 
million until dec 13 1981 when jaruzelski declared martial law 
and jailed thousands of members including walesa solidarity was 
outlawed the following year 
a series of strikes caused by polands collapsing economy last 
