government of national responsibility with the participation of all 
proreformatory political forces represented at the sejm said the 
communique carried on the state pap news agency 
jaruzelski declared that he will urgently consider the 
presented propositions and conduct appropriate consultations aiming 
at the quickest possible appointment of such a government in the 
interest of the nation it said 
walesa and jozwiak expressed satisfaction with the outcome but 
were vague about details apparently not wishing to speak until 
jaruzelski issued his written decision friday 
